<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-05 16:50 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1554 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-CUSTOM-PUBLISH-MEDIA-     09-05 1131
