   PALESTINIAN-PRISONERS_RAMALLAH, West Bank _ Portrait of a
Palestinian family that may soon be touched by the the accord
between the Palestinians and Israelis. The sons of Palestinian
mother Raba Abu Radaha Sunday might soon be released from their
Israeli prison as a result of the new pact. One son, Amir, was
convicted of murdering a Palestinian for helping Israelis. The
other, Sahdi, hit a Jewish woman settler in the head with a bar. To
their family, they are prisoners of a war that is now ending.
