<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-09-05 19:02 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1623 &Cx1f; kan-z
r v BC-BC-KAN-BUDGET-KAN &LR;      09-05 0404
